{"tid":1838883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收皮啦 個撚個連登仔剩係識講樓價跌","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T07:45:14.000Z","uid":258634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0681a9f3a9e04eccd5a54096d530e50fe7ed7ad","tid":1838883,"uid":258634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"首先 而家香港中招⋯⋯仲好心情諗買樓 係都諗點樣喺港共政府嘅領導之下 自救我城先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋就係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔撚會跌呀唔好再FF</span> 首先今次香港唔係全球最嚴重嘅城市 市民無須移民 因為去台灣日本都唔會好過香港幾多 源頭係喺武漢 而其他城市都有人中招<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果要跌到咁誇 係要全世界嘅人都對呢個地方極恐慌 而呢個地裡面嘅人會不顧一切逃走 今次武漢肺炎去到呢個地步嘅地方只有一個 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係武漢</span> 今日嘅武漢就係等同17年前嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以眾巴 想賺錢就而家飛上去武漢買樓啦 我肯定你最少賺幾千萬 甚至幾億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜...你為咗條命唔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但正正因為全世界都唔會咁樣做你先會有發達嘅機會 呢個就係金融同埋經濟 如果你同常人做一樣嘅嘢 係唔會有機會賺錢 所以依家連豬個個都話買樓而你又真係咁傻去買樓 係唔會賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33febf9751613b4219f80637ca7a37a2dfe84c4c","tid":1838883,"uid":203393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"其實見到港共政府咁L樣，留返筆錢移民好過啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd1ee2793056cdece80c4b2febfda40a172c6fc","tid":1838883,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要攬炒</span>"}]}